high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink to your right.
Grab the tomato in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the microwave to your right.
Place the tomato inside the microwave, cook the tomato then remove it.
With the tomato, turn right and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the cooked tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, cross the room, and turn to the right to face the sink.
Pick the tomato up from the sink.
Go to the right and turn around and cross the room to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave and close the door and then open it and take the tomato out again.
Turn to the right and then the right again to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the tomato from in the sink.
Turn right and go forward, then turn right to go to the black table with the microwave on it.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside and heat it up, then take it out.
Turn right and go forward, then turn right to return to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato in the sink.
